---
import CaseStudyLayout from "../layouts/CaseStudyLayout.astro";
---

<CaseStudyLayout
  title="Truist — Digital Banking Platform"
  description="How I built and scaled a 30-person design org at SunTrust across all lines of business, then led business and commercial banking design through the $66B merger to Truist."
  ogImage="/images/truist/1771246115132-cd678175.png"
>
  <style>
    :root {
      --truist-purple: #3b1a5a;
      --truist-deep: #2d1446;
      --truist-teal: #00b4a0;
      --warm-white: #f7f5f2;
      --soft-purple: #f3eff8;
      --text-primary: #1a1a1a;
      --text-secondary: #5a5a5a;
      --text-light: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      --accent: #3b1a5a;
    }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 90vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        #1d0b2e 0%,
        var(--truist-purple) 50%,
        #512678 100%
      );
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 160px 80px;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: -20%;
      right: -10%;
      width: 800px;
      height: 800px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(
        circle,
        rgba(0, 180, 160, 0.1) 0%,
        transparent 70%
      );
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-left {
      max-width: 840px;
      z-index: 1;
      margin-bottom: 80px;
    }

    .hero-right {
      z-index: 1;
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-right img {
      max-height: 520px;
      width: auto;
      border-radius: 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 64px 128px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      background: #000;
    }

    .hero-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--truist-teal);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
      font-size: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-light);
      line-height: 1.75;
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ── Ecosystem Strip ── */
    .ecosystem {
      background: var(--soft-purple);
      padding: 160px 80px;
    }

    .ecosystem-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 40px;
      margin-top: 80px;
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .eco-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 32px rgba(59, 26, 90, 0.05);
      transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
    }

    .eco-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 32px 64px rgba(59, 26, 90, 0.1);
    }

    .eco-card img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .eco-card-text {
      padding: 32px;
    }

    .eco-card-text h3 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .eco-card-text p {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── Dark showcase ── */
    .showcase-dark {
      background: var(--truist-deep);
      padding: 160px 80px;
    }

    .showcase-dark .section-label {
      color: var(--truist-teal);
    }
    .showcase-dark .section-heading {
      color: #fff;
    }
    .showcase-dark .section-body {
      color: var(--text-light);
    }

    .showcase-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 64px;
      margin-top: 80px;
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .showcase-card {
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
    }

    .showcase-card img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .showcase-card-text {
      padding: 32px;
    }

    .showcase-card-text h3 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .showcase-card-text p {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    }

    /* ── Wealth / Enterprise ── */
    .wealth {
      background: var(--warm-white);
      padding: 160px 80px;
    }

    .wealth-hero-img {
      margin-top: 80px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 32px 100px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .wealth-hero-img img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .hero {
        padding: 120px 32px;
      }
      .hero-left {
        margin-bottom: 48px;
      }
      .hero-right img {
        max-height: 480px;
      }
      .ecosystem-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .ecosystem {
        padding: 100px 32px;
      }
      .showcase-dark {
        padding: 100px 32px;
      }
      .showcase-row {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 48px;
      }
      .wealth {
        padding: 100px 32px;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-left">
      <div class="hero-label">Truist Financial</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        Defining the Digital Experience for America's 7th Largest Bank
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        I built and scaled a 30-person design organization at SunTrust — owning
        every line of business — then led business and commercial banking design
        through the largest bank merger since 2008.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-right">
      <img
        src="/images/truist/truist-mobile-app-tour-620x1150.jpg"
        alt="Truist mobile app screens"
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Context -->
  <section class="context">
    <div class="context-inner">
      <div>
        <div class="section-label">The Challenge</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">
          Two legacy banks became one. The digital experience had to earn that
          trust from day one.
        </h2>
        <p class="section-body">
          I inherited a small, nascent UX team at SunTrust with no research
          function, no UI practice, and no independent design voice. I scaled it
          to a 30-person multidisciplinary organization covering consumer, small
          business, wealth management, and commercial banking. When the $66B
          merger with BB&T created Truist, I led business and commercial banking
          design through the transition — rebuilding product experiences for the
          merged entity and translating the new Truist brand into a design
          system deployed across all digital products.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="meta-grid">
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>My Role</h4>
            <p>Head of UX Design &amp; Research</p>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>Company</h4>
            <p>SunTrust → Truist Financial</p>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>Scope</h4>
            <p>
              All lines of business (SunTrust); Business &amp; Commercial
              Banking (Truist); Design System
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>Team</h4>
            <p>UX/UI Designers, Researchers, Product Managers, Engineering</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ecosystem -->
  <div class="ecosystem">
    <div class="section-label">The Ecosystem</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">One design language across every surface.</h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      At SunTrust, I owned every digital touchpoint — consumer mobile, business
      banking, and the web platform. That breadth meant the design system had to
      hold together across radically different use cases and user needs.
    </p>

    <div class="ecosystem-grid">
      <div class="eco-card">
        <img
          src="/images/truist/1771246123096-e2ad64a0.png"
          alt="Truist mobile home screen"
        />
        <div class="eco-card-text">
          <h3>Consumer Mobile</h3>
          <p>
            Account management, transfers, and day-to-day banking designed for
            speed and clarity.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="eco-card">
        <img
          src="/images/truist/f6b34fae57ddb0e3fc45c70cca0e5130.webp"
          alt="Truist business banking dashboard"
        />
        <div class="eco-card-text">
          <h3>Business Banking</h3>
          <p>
            Multi-account management, notifications, and commercial tools for
            business clients.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="eco-card">
        <img
          src="/images/truist/1771246117084-2367c12e.png"
          alt="Truist dashboard on laptop"
        />
        <div class="eco-card-text">
          <h3>Web Platform</h3>
          <p>
            Full-featured dashboard with spending analytics, account activity,
            and cross-product visibility.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Dark Showcase: App Depth -->
  <div class="showcase-dark">
    <div class="section-label">Going Deeper</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">
      The details that make banking feel effortless.
    </h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      Every flow — from transferring money to verifying your identity — was
      designed to reduce friction and build confidence.
    </p>

    <div class="showcase-row">
      <div class="showcase-card">
        <img
          src="/images/truist/1771281467064-e8609008.png"
          alt="Truist app interaction flows"
        />
        <div class="showcase-card-text">
          <h3>Core Interaction Flows</h3>
          <p>
            Transfers, chat, and confirmations — designed as a system, not
            screens.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-card">
        <img
          src="/images/truist/1771281469482-048153c4.png"
          alt="Truist cross-device payments"
        />
        <div class="showcase-card-text">
          <h3>Cross-Device Payments</h3>
          <p>Transfers and QR payments across mobile, web, and wearables.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="showcase-row" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="showcase-card">
        <img
          src="/images/truist/1771281472014-694a3592.png"
          alt="Truist biometric security"
        />
        <div class="showcase-card-text">
          <h3>Biometric Security</h3>
          <p>
            Facial recognition and biometric authentication integrated
            seamlessly into the experience.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-card">
        <img
          src="/images/truist/1771246115132-cd678175.png"
          alt="Truist responsive design system"
        />
        <div class="showcase-card-text">
          <h3>Responsive Design System</h3>
          <p>Consistent brand expression from mobile to desktop to tablet.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Onboarding Feature -->
  <div class="feature-row">
    <div class="feature-image">
      <img
        src="/images/truist/1771281481615-23cda954.jpg"
        alt="Truist onboarding flow on laptop"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="feature-text">
      <div class="section-label">Onboarding</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading">First impressions, done right.</h2>
      <p class="section-body">
        Opening an account is the first real relationship moment. I pushed the
        team to treat onboarding not as a form, but as a conversation —
        progressive disclosure, clear progress, and a sense that the bank
        actually cares about getting to know you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Wealth Management -->
  <section class="wealth">
    <div class="section-label">Wealth Management</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Designing for the highest-value clients.</h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      The wealth management platform required a different register —
      sophisticated, information-dense, and built for clients managing
      substantial portfolios. The same design system, elevated for a different
      audience.
    </p>
    <div class="wealth-hero-img">
      <img
        src="/images/truist/original.png"
        alt="Truist wealth management dashboard"
      />
    </div>
  </section>
</CaseStudyLayout>
